    {\displaystyle v_{j}\,x_{j}\ \geq v_{i}}
   for some 
  
    
      
        
          x
          
            j
          
        
        ∈
        
          Z
          
            +
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle x_{j}\in Z_{+}}
   i.e. 
  
    
      
        J
        =
        {
        j
        }
        ,
        α
        =
        1
        ,
        
          x
          
            j
          
        
